


jwt-gin-postgres/
├── cmd/                    # Application entry points
│   └── main.go            # Main application file
├── internal/              # Private application code
│   ├── config/           # Configuration management
│   │   └── config.go     # App configuration
│   ├── database/         # Database interactions
│   │   └── postgres.go   # PostgreSQL connection and queries
│   ├── handlers/         # HTTP request handlers
│   │   └── auth.go       # Authentication endpoints
│   ├── middleware/       # HTTP middleware
│   │   └── auth.go       # JWT verification middleware
│   ├── models/           # Data models
│   │   └── user.go       # User model and validations
│   └── utils/            # Helper functions
│       └── password.go   # Password hashing utilities
├── .env                  # Env variable
└── go.mod                # Go module definition




Client ---> API Request (access token)
            |
            | Access token valid?
            | Yes --> API responds 200 OK
            | No  --> API responds 401 Unauthorized
            v
Client detects 401 --> Calls /refresh with refresh token
            |
            v
Server validates refresh token
            |
            v
New access token issued
            |
            v
Client retries original API request with new access token
